# ToDo 2: Verify files created and compare to link: https://docs.chef.io/chef_repo/
ls -al ~/chef-repo

# ToDo 4: Configure knife
knife configure
- Enter Chef server URL: add organization to what is presented: https://ip-172-31-8-38.ec2.internal/organizations/simple
- Enter an existing username: <enter username from Exercise 3.1, ToDo 1>

# ToDo 5: Configure SSL for knife and chef and verify trusted certs ~/.chef/trusted_certs
knife ssl check

# ToDo 6: List API Clients (created organization) and organization validator
knife client list

